OL,13,FHaving a mortgage used to seem like an
OL,14,Fappealing alternative to renting
OL,15,Fprivately from a landlord. In the years
OL,16,Fafter the global financial crisis of
OL,17,F2008, ultra-low interest rates meant
OL,18,Fborrowing was kept cheap and owning a
OL,19,Fhome was generally less expensive than
OL,20,Frenting one.
OL,3,CThe government's mortgage interest
OL,4,Csupport falls seriously short. They
OL,5,Cneed to increase it.
